high_descs: turn left, face counter with coffee maker
pick up white mug from coffee maker
turn left, go to microwave above stove
place mug on right side of microwave, microwave mug, remove mug from microwave, close microwave
turn around, go to small black shelves at left end of counter to the left
place mug in between dispenser and tomato on black shelves
anns.task_desc: place microwaved mug on shelves to the left of counter

high_descs: Turn to the coffee pot on your left.
Remove the coffee mug from the front of the coffee maker.
Turn to your left and go to the microwave across the room, above the stove.
Place the coffee cup in the microwave, heat it up, then remove the coffee cup from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right at the door, and go to the small, black shelf across from you.
Place the coffee mug on the top of the small, black, shelf, to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm coffee mug on the shelf.

high_descs: Take a small step forward then turn left to face the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug that's in front of you.
Turn left and take two steps to your left then walk to the stove and stand in front of it facing it.
Look up and warm the mug in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the door then turn right and walk to the black table.
Put the mug to the left of the soap dispenser.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug on the table.
